riting them — all coming at it from a JavaScript angle.","md","en",{},"\u002Fen\u002Fpython\u002Flearn-python-from-javascript-05-functions","8",{"title":6,"description":2054},false,"en\u002FPython\u002Flearn-python-from-javascript-05-functions",[2052,2064,2065,2066],"JavaScript","Learn Python From JavaScript","第 13 屆 iT邦幫忙鐵人賽",null,"\u002Fen\u002Fpython\u002F2021\u002F09\u002F06\u002Flearn-python-from-javascript-05-functions\u002F","VLG9ifEIeMAYzwLQs41I6RTshhqOy_ofIQJKa0f6TzE",{"newer":2071,"older":2075},{"url":2072,"title":2073,"date":2074},"\u002Fen\u002Fpython\u002F2021\u002F09\u002F07\u002Fpython-from-js-06-variable-scope\u002F","Learning Python From a JavaScript Angle (6) - Variable Scope","2021-09-07 00:00:10",{"url":2076,"title":2077,"date":2078},"\u002Fen\u002Fpython\u002F2021\u002F09\u002F05\u002Fjs-to-python-04-types-and-variables\u002F","Learning Python From a JavaScript Angle (4) - Types and Variables","2021-09-05 00:00:10",[2080,2085,2090],{"url":2081,"title":2082,"date":2083,"readingMinutes":2084},"\u002Fen\u002Fpython\u002F2021\u002F10\u002F02\u002Flearn-python-from-javascript-31-finale\u002F","Learning Python from a JavaScript Angle (31): So What Do You Want to Learn Next?","2021-10-02 00:00:05","4",{"url":2086,"title":2087,"date":2088,"readingMinutes":2089},"\u002Fen\u002Fpython\u002F2021\u002F10\u002F01\u002Flearning-python-from-javascript-30-web-scraping\u002F","Learning Python From JavaScript (30): Building a Web Scraper","2021-10-01 00:00:10","6",{"url":2091,"title":2092,"date":2093,"readingMinutes":2089},"\u002Fen\u002Fpython\u002F2021\u002F09\u002F30\u002Fpython-29-beautifulsoup\u002F","Learning Python From a JavaScript Angle (29) - BeautifulSoup","2021-09-30 00:00:10",1784011709895]